<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1827] Add disabling block cache scanner flag to the shell, option for scan and count</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1827</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1823&quot; title=&quot;Ability for Scanners to bypass the block cache&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-1823&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-1823&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; added an option for individual Scans to not cache blocks.  Expose this as an option in the shell for scan and count.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
